<h2>A New Hero For a New World</h2>
<p>Begin a brand new adventure in <em>FATE: The Cursed King</em>, the fourth game in WildTangent’s popular dungeon-crawling series. Explore the catacombs and castles of Ekbatan on a quest to banish the ultimate undead evil. Recruit NPC allies, trade special items, and earn achievements through Facebook!</p>
<ul>
<li>Epic RPG - all ages/skill levels</li>
<li>New party system</li>
<li>Gorgeous new setting</li>
<li>Fully mod-able</li>
</ul>
